	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Qui has perferendas accepit<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Der Briefüberbringer ist unbekannt.</note>, nunc est civis Argentinę, vir tui valde observans.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dicit se initio praedicationis <persName ref="265">Zvinglii</persName><note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2"><persName ref="265">Zwingli</persName> predigte vom 1. Januar 1519 an in Zürich, s. HBRG I 12f.</note>, si recte memini, aut certe sub primum bellum patrium<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Gemeint ist der Erste Kappelerkrieg vom Juni 1529, s. HBLS IV 455.</note> factum extorrem a <placeName ref="652">Lucerna</placeName> propter causam communem.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Eum, oro, juves.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">A <persName ref="154">Myconio</persName> causam omnem intelliges<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Ein entsprechendes Schreiben von <persName ref="154">Myconius</persName> ist nicht bekannt.</note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto"><pb type="edition" next="480"/>Age vero, mi Bullingere, quanto testimonio quidam apud nos prędicant tuam diligentiam et studium in concordia ecclesiarum reparanda!</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Idem et <persName ref="28">Bucerus</persName> agnoscit.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nos adhuc bona spes tenet.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nam operam dabimus, ut Witenbergenses et principes intelligant, quam plene veritatem agnoscatis et quam minime contemnendus metus ab articulis<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Gemeint ist die <placeName ref="1205">Wittenberger</placeName> Konkordie (BucerDS VI/I 114-134).</note> recipiendis vos remoretur.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Omnia synceriter et ut in oculis domini admoliemur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale felicissime.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Leonem<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6"><persName ref="114">Leo Jud</persName>.</note>, <persName ref="14">Bibliandrum</persName>, <persName ref="165">Pellicanum</persName> nostrum, amicos omnes salvere plurimum opto.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Argen[torati]30. novembris anno 1536.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">V. <persName ref="40">Capito</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo d. Henrico Bullingero, pastori Tigurino, sibi in domino observando.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
